Okay as I’m going into official con crunch I am going to post my lineup as I always do :3 I’m super excited to go again this year as least year was really really fun! 
.
Friday-
I’m starting the day as Kanade! I’m whipping out her I nandesu card and I’m really excited to have it made!  I’ll be going to the project Sekai meetup because I want to meet more people as Brainrot as me XD 
.
In the afternoon, I’ll be xayah in a christmas version! I’ll be matching with @leviathancosplays who will be my Rakan. It’ll be my Christmas themed cosplay for the weekend :3 
.
Saturday-
I’ll start as Irida from Pokémon legends arceus! I’ll be matching with @tsumetaikarite who will be Adaman and we will be going to the Pokémon meetup! :3
.
Mid day I’ll be bringing back a cosplay from good old 2020, Mirai Miku 2020! This is a cosplay I’ve always wanted to wear to a con so this is the perfect time to bring her!
.
The night time I’ll be in bunny Marin! It’s def my late night cosplay as this one has a lot to show XD 
.
Sunday-
I’ll be Ranko from Akiba maid war! I’m actually super excited tor this one cause this anime has to be one of my all time favs now XD 
.
The afternoon once we are chill we will be at the pool and I’ll do a shoot in Marin swimsuit! It’s not her canon one but a different design I found that I liked! Plus I want to enjoy the pool this year :3
.
